#DESCRIPTION
##  Algebra: Properties of polynomial functions
##ENDDESCRIPTION


## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Polynomial equations and functions)
## DBsection(Inequalities involving polynomials)
## Date(01/07/2010)
## Institution(University of Minnesota)
